biotools.summary: Soybean context-specific network analysis and prediction based on tissue-specific transcriptome data | SoyCSN (Soybean Context Specific Network) - | SoyCSN (Soybean Context Specific Network) | SoyCSN computes and visualizes any of the 14 soybean context specific networks both at the expression and interactome level. Users can compare the gene-gene relationship differences at different confidence levels across all the soybean tissues
